Virtual CSO Implementation Guide ŌĆö Step-by-Step n8n Build-Out  
Let me walk you through exactly how to implement this system, phase by phase, with specific n8n workflow structures and validation steps.

Implementation Philosophy  
Build Order Principle: Test Early, Test Often  
We're going to build in this sequence:

Simplest piece first (Agent 1 as standalone)  
Validate it works (unit test with real queries)  
Add next piece (Agent 2\)  
Validate integration (test Agent 1 ŌåÆ Agent 2\)  
Continue until full system is operational

Why this matters: If you build all 4 workflows and then test, debugging becomes a nightmare. Building incrementally means when something breaks, you know exactly where.

