Node 4: Supabase Query  
sqlSELECT   
    chunk\_id,  
    content,  
    stage,  
    domain,  
    content\_type,  
    kpi\_family,  
    source\_doc,  
    chunk\_summary,  
    1 \- (embedding \<=\> CAST($1 AS vector)) AS similarity\_score  
FROM kb\_platform\_knowledge  
WHERE   
    \-- Stage filter  
    (stage \= $2 OR stage \= 'all')  
      
    \-- Content type filter (if provided)  
    AND (  
        $3::text\[\] IS NULL   
        OR content\_type \= ANY($3::text\[\])  
    )  
      
    \-- Domain filter (if provided)  
    AND (  
        $4::text\[\] IS NULL   
        OR domain \= ANY($4::text\[\])  
        OR domain \= 'cross\_domain'  
    )  
      
    \-- KPI family filter (if provided)  
    AND (  
        $5 IS NULL   
        OR kpi\_family \= $5  
    )

ORDER BY embedding \<=\> CAST($1 AS vector)  
LIMIT $6;  
Parameters:

$1: {{ $json.embedding }} (from OpenAI node)  
$2: {{ $json.stage\_filter }}  
$3: {{ $json.content\_type\_filter }} (convert to PostgreSQL array format: {benchmark,framework\_definition})  
$4: {{ $json.domain\_filter }}  
$5: {{ $json.kpi\_family\_filter }}  
$6: {{ $json.max\_chunks }}

